send_unflip_as_message: 发送 ┬─┬ノ( º_ºノ) 作为消息
start_direct_message_with_user: 与用户开始私聊。示例：/startdm userId1
join_room_with_address: 使用地址加入房间。示例：/join address1 address2
invite_user_to_room: 邀请用户到房间。示例：/invite userId1 userId2 [-r reason]
disinvite_user_to_room: 取消邀请用户到房间。示例：/disinvite userId1 userId2 [-r reason]
kick_user_from_room: 从房间踢出用户。示例：/kick userId1 userId2 servername [-r reason]
ban_user_from_room: 禁止用户进入房间。示例：/ban userId1 userId2 servername [-r reason]
unban_user_from_room: 取消禁止用户进入房间。示例：/unban userId1 userId2
ignore_user: 忽略用户。示例：/ignore userId1 userId2
unignore_user: 取消忽略用户。示例：/unignore userId1 userId2
change_profile_picture_in_current_room: 在当前房间更改头像。示例 /myroomavatar mxc://xyzabc
delete_messages_from_users: 删除用户的消息。示例：/delete userId1 servername -past 1d|2h|5m|30s [-t m.room.message] [-r spam]
manage_server_access_control_list: 管理服务器访问控制列表。示例 /acl [-a servername1] [-d servername2] [-ra servername1] [-rd servername2]
